    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_3459409165" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3459409165" />
    <a title="John" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19510801-john"><img alt="John" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3459409165?book_show_action=true">Sep 23, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="John" class="user" itemprop="url" name="John" href="/user/show/19510801-john">John</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/19510801-john?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/19510801-john?shelf=acquired-waiting-to-be-read">acquired-waiting-to-be-read</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3459409165" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5534756493214427977">I make no bones about it, I love the Newford books. This was one of the hardest to read, only partly because of the small font size in the edition I had, but also because it deals with lots of aspects of the dreamlands and the relationships with the “World-As-It-Is” Jilly is one of my favourite characters and this is essentially her story. I really enjoyed it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


